          <div class="timeline-item" data-year="2015">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-year">2015</div>
              <h3>The Challenge</h3>
              <p>
                Discovered Dark Souls. Died to the first boss 47 times.
                Got back up 48 times. Fell in love with the grind.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Timeline Item 3 -->
          <div class="timeline-item" data-year="2018">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-year">2018</div>
              <h3>The Evolution</h3>
              <p>
                Started streaming my attempts at beating tough bosses.
                People actually enjoyed watching me struggle. Who knew?
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Timeline Item 4 -->
          <div class="timeline-item" data-year="2020">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-year">2020</div>
              <h3>The Community</h3>
              <p>
                Launched Tricky P Gaming officially. Built a community of
                gamers who love a challenge as much as I do.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Timeline Item 5 -->
          <div class="timeline-item" data-year="2025">
            <div class="timeline-marker active"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-year">2025</div>
              <h3>The Adventure Continues</h3>
              <p>
                Still here, still grinding, still loving every minute.
                And this is just the beginning.
              </p>
